snippet: American intelligence agencies have discovered that North Korea is moving mobile missile launchers around the country, some carrying a new generation of powerful rocket.
abstract: American intelligence agencies discover that North Korea is moving mobile missile launchers around country, some carrying new generation of powerful rocket that has yet to be operationally deployed; move brings into question intention of young leader Kim Jong-un.

byline.original: By THOM SHANKER and DAVID E. SANGER

lead_paragraph: American intelligence agencies have discovered that North Korea is moving mobile missile launchers around the country, some carrying a new generation of powerful rocket.

headline.seo: North Korea’s Missile Movements Worry U.S.
headline.main: Movement of Missiles by North Korea Worries U.S.
